		<h1>Main</h1>
		<p>LUSI (Library for Sourcecode Install) is a library to install/uninstall/update sourcecode packages. The intention is automatize as much as possible the configure/build/install routine and future uninstallations or updates.</p>
		<p>It is licensed under the <a href="http://www.gnu.org/copyleft/gpl.html" title="GNU General Public License page">GNU GPL license</a>. It is also free as in "free beer".</p>
